patthana16.74:4.1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ ajjhattikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.74:4.2: Anidassanaappaṭighaṃ ajjhattikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pe …
patthana16.74:4.4: anidassanaappaṭighaṃ ajjhattikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko ca naanidassanasappaṭigho naajjhattiko ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana16.74:5.1: Anidassanasappaṭighaṃ bāhiraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho nabāhiro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.74:5.3: Hetuyā ekādasa, ārammaṇe tīṇi … pe … avigate ekādasa.
